videos.description: BYU guard Elijah Bryant drives down the lane and rises up for an uncontested two-handed dunk for the game's first points.
videos.headline: BYU's Bryant jams to open game

videos.description: With the clock winding down in the third quarter, Stanford's Oscar da Silva uses the backboard to bank home his 3, extending the Cardinal's lead.
videos.headline: Stanford banks in buzzer-beating triple
